parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Unusual noises
vibrations
or grinding sounds from the undercarriage
loss of power
hesitation
or stalling
warning lights illuminated on the dashboard
including the "Service 4WD" or "PTU" light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate, stall, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Delayed or hesitant shifting
unusual noises or vibrations
warning lights illuminated on the dashboard
including the "Check Engine" or "Transmission" light
loss of power
or stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Unusual noises or vibrations from the rear of the vehicle
loss of power
hesitation
or stalling
warning lights illuminated on the dashboard
including the "Service 4WD" or "Rear Differential" light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and shifter can cause the vehicle to hesitate, stall, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Unusual noises or vibrations from the clutch or shifter
difficulty shifting gears
warning lights illuminated on the dashboard
including the "Service Shifter" light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPB can cause the parking brake to engage unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries. Water intrusion into the liftgate module can also cause a fire hazard.
symptoms: The parking brake engages unexpectedly
the parking brake light comes on
the vehicle cannot be flat towed
water leaks into the liftgate module
corrosion of the EPB module
moldy seats and carpet due to water intrusion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The service shifter error can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The service shifter light comes on
the shifter wiring harness needs to be replaced
the speedometer is obscured while traveling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repair can cause a fire hazard, as the vehicle cannot be parked indoors or near other vehicles.
symptoms: The part to do the recall repair is not yet available
the manufacturer has exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the vehicle cannot be parked indoors or near other vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle shutting down while driving can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down completely while driving
the vehicle is unsafe to drive until the matter is completely fixed or replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power liftgate module can cause the liftgate to malfunction, leading to potential fires and safety risks.
symptoms: The liftgate sometimes works and sometimes does not
requiring a "reset" by pulling the fuse and disconnecting the battery
and may not lock or lower properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The service shifter light issue can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The service shifter light comes on
often accompanied by other warning lights
and can cause the vehicle to shut off or become difficult to shift.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission and drivetrain issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The transmission may lag
jump
or hesitate
and the vehicle may shut off or become difficult to shift.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failures can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may shut off or experience electrical issues
such as the 4WD light coming on
and may be accompanied by other warning lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The PTU module failure can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The PTU module may short circuit
causing the drivetrain control module to fail
and may require replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The recall issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience issues related to recalls
such as the 2.4L In-use NOx catalyst efficiency recall
and may not have the necessary parts available for repair.
